txt.en: The recipe needed to complete this quest is available for purchase. <rgb=#00f000>Purchase the quest recipe from the guild leader.</rgb>\n\nCreate a crate of cooked food for Umbar Baharbêl.
Provide the cooked plates to the Umbar Cook's Guild Leader.
Deliver a crate of food to the Umbar Cook's Guild Leader
Talk to the Cook's Guild Leader in Umbar Baharbêl
'Most excellent. This food will satisfy the needs of innkeeps in the lower quarters.'
Deliver a crate of food to the Umbar Cook's Guild Leader
Turn in ([placeholder]/[placeholder]) rationed seasoned fish platters to the Umbar Cook's Guild Leader
'Most excellent. These rationed seasoned fish platters will satisfy the needs of guards throughout Umbar Baharbêl.'
Talk to the Cook's Guild Leader in Umbar Baharbêl
Turn in ([placeholder]/[placeholder]) Umbari feasts to the Umbar Cook's Guild Leader
Talk to the Cook's Guild Leader in Umbar Baharbêl
Craft a crate of cooked food for the Umbar Cook's Guild
'Most excellent. These Umbari feasts will satisfy the needs of the wealthy throughout Umbar Baharbêl.'
Executed the recipe for a crate of cooked food
The cook's guild in Umbar Baharbêl supplies foodstuff to taverns, the Kindred, and everyone in between. They require assistance with meeting the demands of the people.
Crafted a crate of cooked food for the Umbar Cook's Guild
Executed the recipe for a seasoned fish platter ([placeholder]/6)
Execute the recipe for a crate of cooked food

'Good day to you. I am pleased that you have joined our guild. I am grateful you are willing to assist us with meeting the demands placed upon the guild. Food is a tie that binds together the lowliest and the wealthiest and we meet the requests of all.\n\n'As a member, we look to you to assist us in meeting requests set forth by the ever-demanding populace. Are you prepared to do your part?'
